body:
**Updates:**

1. ConfigNode and DataNode now will log their environment variables at the begining of startup like below:
```
## ConfigNode
2023-01-11 10:55:42,558 [main] INFO  o.a.i.c.s.ConfigNode:81 - IoTDB-ConfigNode environment variables:
	CONFIGNODE_HOME=./..;
	CONFIGNODE_CONF=./../conf;

## DataNode
2023-01-11 10:55:47,045 [main] INFO  o.a.i.db.service.DataNode:141 - IoTDB-DataNode environment variables:
	IOTDB_HOME=./..;
	IOTDB_CONF=./../conf;
	IOTDB_DATA_HOME=./..;
```
2. Formatting configuration variables output:
```
2023-01-11 10:55:48,081 [main] INFO  o.a.i.db.service.DataNode:174 - IoTDB configuration variables:
	WATERMARK_GROUPED_LSB=GroupBasedLSBMethod;
	CONFIG_NAME=iotdb-datanode.properties;
	logger=Logger[org.apache.iotdb.db.conf.IoTDBConfig];
        ...
```
